metadata.name: FREE - JED XO
metadata.description:
"Free" is a song that I wrote about cherishing the things in life that truly matter. It's a reminder to take a step back and appreciate the simple things that we often take for granted - things like the ability to breathe, the beauty of nature, and the love of our loved ones. These are things that cannot be bought, no matter how much wealth we accumulate.  
This song is a result of one of my web3 collaborations. The beat was expertly crafted by Senseishui, a talented producer that I met through Twitter spaces. The artwork for the song was created by me using the AI tool Midjourney, adding an extra layer of personal touch to the project.  
When you listen to this song, I hope you can deeply relate to the message it conveys and take a moment to appreciate the free things in life that truly matter.
